Note: ============================================================================

@Reasoning:
Bare identifier reference -> HIR identifier node. The name resolution
(local vs nonlocal vs global vs builtin) is left to a later pass — this
translator just produces the structural node with the captured name
string.
@End Reasoning
Process called "translate_identifier" takes context as Integer, node as Integer returns Integer:
    Note: Translate identifier to HIR

